        "text": [
          "ه عن القاسم بن عروة فقد رويته عن أبي- رضي اللّه عنه- عن عبد اللّه ابن جعفر الحميريّ، عن هارون بن مسلم بن سعدان، عن القاسم بن عروة."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Al-Qasim ibn Urwah has been transmitted by me from my father - may Allah (swt) be pleased with him - from Abdullah ibn Jafar Al-Himyari, from Harun ibn Muslim ibn Sadan, from Al-Qasim ibn Urwah."
          ]
